  <article>
    <p id="para1">What is the A/V Club?</p>
    <p id="para2">The AV Club is a space where anyone interested in the Audio-Visual world can learn more about it. In this club we'll discuss all things pop-culture currently going on. The goal is to create a community of content creators, whether that is filmmaking or podcasting, and people who appreciate all types of media such as, music, sports, etc. This club watches movies, creates a fellowship of like-minded content creators, and assists members in anyway possible.</p>
